Comment: 0,0:01:09.67,0:01:11.97,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just begun.
Comment: 0,0:01:11.97,0:01:13.94,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we go full speed and funky beat.
Comment: 0,0:01:13.94,0:01:15.67,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll surely shine.
Comment: 0,0:01:15.67,0:01:17.57,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Around the world.
Comment: 0,0:01:17.57,0:01:18.52,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Trip to the world.
Comment: 0,0:01:18.52,0:01:20.42,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Ho! Here we go to an unknown world.
