Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.42,0:01:40.22,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with this Eight-Six?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.22,0:01:44.56,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,These normal wheels make me\Nsick just looking at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.60,0:01:48.32,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,My eyes are watering!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.32,0:01:51.83,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen someone\Ndriving an Eight-Five!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.83,0:01:54.48,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,A brat deserves an Eight-Five!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.53,0:02:03.09,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Try hard and don't let\Na scooter tailgate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.68,0:02:09.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pissed.  I can't let them\Nget away with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.79,0:02:10.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.84,0:02:18.05,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta...Takumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.05,0:02:20.27,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Taku...Taku...Taku...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.76,0:02:22.47,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,My...my...my Eight-Five...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.47,0:02:26.56,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Please drive gently with my Eight-Five!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.36,0:02:31.18,TITLE,,0340,0000,0128,,{\fad(1000,1040)\blur1.5\pos(212,303)}Dangerous Shingo Appears!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.36,0:02:31.18,TITLE,,0340,0000,0128,,{\fad(1000,1040)\blur1.5\pos(212,277)}ACT.11
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.99,0:02:42.41,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright, Takumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.87,0:02:45.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,T...Takumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.46,0:02:50.88,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,S...stop, Takumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.86,0:03:19.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice move!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:35.46,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.39,0:03:41.26,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, a car's tailgating us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.26,0:03:42.84,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be those Akina brats.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.84,0:03:46.26,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll need ten years of\Npractice to challenge us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.46,0:03:52.01,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.01,0:03:54.27,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll outrun it easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.00,0:04:12.92,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi, it's alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.92,0:04:14.97,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,STOP!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.52,0:04:32.81,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,SLOW DOWN, TAKUMI!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.12,0:04:54.66,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.66,0:04:57.56,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really my Eight-Five?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.87,0:05:04.43,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The car behind us is pretty good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:06.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.93,0:05:09.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what's goin' on,\Nbut that's the Eight-Five!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.42,0:05:11.31,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the Eight-Five we\Nsaw at the top earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.31,0:05:15.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be!  How could an Eight-Five\Nkeep up with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.87,0:05:24.53,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Y...you're right!\NIt's that Eight-Five!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.53,0:05:26.71,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Those brats must've lied to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:28.83,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.83,0:05:30.54,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...an Eight-Six!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.53,0:05:32.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Okay, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.46,0:05:38.09,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}What's this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.09,0:05:41.38,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}It doesn't accelerate,\Neven on the downhill.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.84,0:05:44.26,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}And the tires...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.26,0:05:48.22,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I don't believe this.\NThey don't have any grip at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.93,0:05:56.06,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He's incredibly fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.06,0:05:58.52,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}It's so slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.90,0:06:02.76,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Oh well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.76,0:06:05.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}...I don't have any choice\Nbut to do it that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.39,0:06:30.06,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you pass, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.48,0:06:33.43,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.27,0:06:39.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.58,0:06:41.63,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,How I was overtaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:44.46,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not an Eight-Five...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.46,0:06:46.73,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...it must be an Eight-Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.73,0:06:49.97,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,A highly tuned Eight-Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.41,0:06:57.14,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Or so I thought, but that rolling...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.14,0:07:00.72,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Could that really be an Eight-Five?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.64,0:07:15.07,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We were totally outrun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.07,0:07:17.05,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That Eight-Five gave me the creeps!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.05,0:07:18.47,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Could that be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.32,0:07:23.11,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...A GHOST?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.30,0:07:27.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Is coffee alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.43,0:07:31.37,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.37,0:07:32.43,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Arigato.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.85,0:07:37.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I understand what Iketani meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.74,0:07:40.11,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Your downhill driving is unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.11,0:07:41.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.60,0:07:44.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.30,0:07:47.63,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You dummy.\NYou just don't know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.63,0:07:52.27,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought a car\Ncould run like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:56.91,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,My point of view has been changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.91,0:07:59.32,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It was so shocking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.32,0:08:01.52,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it that scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.52,0:08:02.65,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.65,0:08:04.76,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to apologize, Takumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.76,0:08:08.73,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy I can't sit still.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.24,0:08:14.66,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The performance of a car isn't the issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.97,0:08:20.08,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Good skill can make an Eight-Five\Nrun fast like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.53,0:08:25.36,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I really like this car a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.36,0:08:30.05,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take good care of it, and I'll practice\Nhard starting tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.97,0:08:36.72,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind if people laugh at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.72,0:08:40.40,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I like my Eight-Five best.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.78,0:08:44.76,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.76,0:08:48.78,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's ask some girls to go\Ndriving in my Eight-Five.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.78,0:08:49.46,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,S...sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:52.32,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go without telling\Nme next time, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.32,0:08:54.25,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what, Takumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.25,0:08:55.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.33,0:08:59.63,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Beach, girls in swimsuits...\NWait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.46,0:09:17.98,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.69,0:09:23.57,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,My S13...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.57,0:09:27.84,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, it's returned with the\Nsame handsome face as before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.84,0:09:30.07,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm almost ready to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.45,0:09:33.49,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Itsuki, are you trying to run me over?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.02,0:09:37.69,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start driving hard tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.69,0:09:40.70,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lower the grade of the tires\Nand practice drifting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.70,0:09:42.46,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll join you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.88,0:09:45.38,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this sticker!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.75,0:09:51.49,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.49,0:09:54.14,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.25,0:09:59.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Manager, look at this.{\r}\NI'm finally a member of the Speedstars!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:10:01.35,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Hm...you'd better get it off.{\r}\NAlright, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.35,0:10:05.53,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Maybe I can smooth it out...{\r}\NAnd before I forget the feeling of\Nthe downhill drive with Takumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.53,0:10:06.63,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.63,0:10:09.14,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You rode with Takumi in his Eight-Six?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.14,0:10:10.84,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I did...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.84,0:10:13.80,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...but not in his Eight-Six though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:16.77,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that suspicious grin?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.77,0:10:18.43,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:19.59,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.59,0:10:21.52,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to drink oil, Itsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.52,0:10:24.38,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.38,0:10:30.63,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I let him drive my Eight-Five, and he\Npushed it hard on Akina's downhill.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.63,0:10:34.85,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It was incredible!  I've never had\Nsuch an experience before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.85,0:10:38.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,My Eight-Five started skidding\Nway before the corner...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.82,0:10:43.26,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...and the reflection on the windshield\Nwent by sideways so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.26,0:10:45.14,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a godsent skill!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.14,0:10:47.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He drifted your Eight-Five?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:49.69,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't even have LSD.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.69,0:10:52.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It happened so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.10,0:10:56.17,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He passed two cars, driven by jerks\Nin the hairpins on the downhill.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:59.58,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It felt so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.58,0:11:04.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you believe that story, Manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.00,0:11:07.05,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's Takumi, it's just\Nan ordinary Eight-Five.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.05,0:11:12.72,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Usually, it'd be impossible,\Nsince it's an Eight-Five.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.72,0:11:14.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to say that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.60,0:11:17.68,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you don't believe me,\Nfact is fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:22.65,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If he can do that with\Nan Eight-Five...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.65,0:11:29.46,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...he has much better adaptability\Nthan I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:34.27,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The Eight-Five and Eight-Six share the same body,\Nso maybe the characteristics are similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.27,0:11:35.86,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.86,0:11:37.65,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The suspension of a normal Eight-Five...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.65,0:11:43.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Bunta's heavily tuned Eight-Six\Nare like chocolate and shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.20,0:11:44.25,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,They're totally different.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.25,0:11:46.21,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Chocolate and... shit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.21,0:11:49.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So Takumi can push\Nany car to the limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.74,0:11:50.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:57.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he can push any car with\Nan FR layout to its full potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.76,0:12:02.52,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that you can't use any\Ntricks to drive the Eight-Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.52,0:12:07.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to master the basics\Nin order to push it to the limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.00,0:12:10.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The Eight-Six is a car\Nthat trains the driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.10,0:12:12.90,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what Bunta always says.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.68,0:12:43.51,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The car that just passed by\Nhad a Night Kids sticker.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.51,0:12:46.02,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It had the suspension\Nof a road racer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.74,0:12:48.84,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If you pay attention to\Nhow a car bounces...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.84,0:12:52.71,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...it's easy to tell whether the\Nsuspension is modified or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.86,0:12:58.78,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, we've seen the Night Kids\Nso often on Akina lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.15,0:13:00.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why they come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.11,0:13:05.83,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, their leader, Nakazato,\Nwas defeated...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.83,0:13:10.48,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I don't think anyone will ask\Nfor a return match.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.37,0:13:27.16,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It serves him right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.16,0:13:32.80,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,After being defeated by the Eight-Six, Takeshi\Nwon't be so influential in the team anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.04,0:13:34.38,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What would you like to have?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.75,0:13:37.01,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Two coffees.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.01,0:13:37.51,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Okay.{\r}\NTwo coffees.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.51,0:13:42.29,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, Shingo, I heard that the driver\Nof the Speedstars' Eight-Six is young.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.49,0:13:46.01,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know about him...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.01,0:13:51.25,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I defeat the Eight-Six, then me and\NTakeshi's positions will be reversed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.25,0:13:54.51,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be the fastest of the Night Kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.51,0:13:56.08,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to do it, Shingo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.08,0:14:00.29,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're fast on the downhill,\Nbut your opponent won't be so easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:05.99,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be able to equal him by racing\Nnormally, but that'd be boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:09.19,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I have an interesting idea that will guarantee\Na 100 percent chance of winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.65,0:14:11.87,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait and see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.87,0:14:16.19,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...and I'll let him experience an\Nimpressive and dangerous downhill.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.53,0:14:20.07,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only room for one downhill specialist\Nand that should be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.80,0:14:23.46,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The days of the Eight-Six are over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.46,0:14:27.61,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll push it to the bottom of the valley\Nand send it to the junkyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.57,0:14:37.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoji Shingo of the Night Kids is the fastest\Ndownhill driver in the Gunma area.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.32,0:14:58.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Ryosuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.24,0:15:00.66,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.66,0:15:04.70,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He's staying in his room, staring at\Nhis computer every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.34,0:15:07.58,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what's so interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.58,0:15:14.25,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,No other Road Racer in Gunma could use a\Ncomputer to race faster, except my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.51,0:15:24.33,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hiroshi, what do you think would happen\Nif Akina's Eight-Six and my brother raced?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.33,0:15:26.18,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I think?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.18,0:15:28.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way Ryosuke would be defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.39,0:15:34.58,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The Eight-Six's secrets are out in the\Nopen because of the last race.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.58,0:15:38.34,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,All data was registered systematically\Nin Ryosuke's brain...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.34,0:15:41.40,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...and he must've completed\Na winning simulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.50,0:15:49.62,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,No other Road Racer knows\Ncars better than my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.62,0:15:51.78,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,His technique is outclassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.78,0:15:55.05,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't imagine my brother being defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:56.37,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.06,0:16:00.47,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But I feel like the Eight-Six\Nwon't be defeated either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.32,0:16:08.92,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful high speed drift...\NExquisite braking control...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.92,0:16:10.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He's equally exceptional.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.56,0:16:18.24,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,As a Road Racer, driving the FR layout,\Nmaybe I'm addicted to his driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.24,0:16:19.49,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Keisuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.49,0:16:22.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If they race, one of them will lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:24.94,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want my brother to be defeated...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.94,0:16:29.34,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...but for some reason, I also don't want\Nto see the Eight-Six defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:31.66,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Odd, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.28,0:16:36.09,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.09,0:16:37.84,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get wet?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.84,0:16:38.51,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.51,0:16:40.04,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Pick it up for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.41,0:16:45.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi, why don't we go somewhere again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.39,0:16:51.85,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The mountains, highlands or\Nthe beach would be nice, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.73,0:16:54.31,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.36,0:16:59.68,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll share a lot of memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.99,0:17:01.53,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.19,0:17:06.84,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's with you....
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.84,0:17:08.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...I don't mind staying overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.23,0:17:19.44,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,When will you have a day off?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.44,0:17:21.04,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Sunday again...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.04,0:17:23.57,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The schedule's not up yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.46,0:17:28.16,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't we go driving\Non the next holiday?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.16,0:17:31.19,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,With your car.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.87,0:17:39.07,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Don't go without telling\Nme next time, Takumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.69,0:17:43.91,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Ummm...do you mind if Itsuki\Ncomes along, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.59,0:17:45.87,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Itsuki, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.28,0:17:47.04,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:51.87,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can arrange a girl for him,\Nit would be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.32,0:17:57.80,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a nice guy, but he's clumsy\Nabout finding a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.19,0:18:02.26,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a really good friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.26,0:18:05.72,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mean to be like this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.00,0:18:13.06,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll talk to my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.06,0:18:14.77,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You will?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.63,0:18:19.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find a pretty girl who matches Itsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.98,0:18:51.71,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You look cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.71,0:18:54.19,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'd better give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.19,0:18:57.88,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting better at using the parking\Nbrake to let the rear skid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.88,0:19:01.11,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Steering timing is the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.11,0:19:05.59,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So you use the parking\Nbrake to start drifting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.29,0:19:10.34,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Iketani, when I was sitting\Nnext to Takumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.34,0:19:14.06,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...I didn't see him using\Nthe parking brake at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.06,0:19:19.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi has an advanced technique to initiate\Nthe load-shift by only using the foot brake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.00,0:19:22.95,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a long way to go\Nto achieve that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.92,0:19:29.89,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been happy skidding our cars by stepping\Non the gas pedal at a corner's exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.89,0:19:35.05,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's an elementary technique called\N"power slide," and it's different from a drift.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.44,0:19:39.04,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,In a real drift, like you see\NTakumi doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.04,0:19:43.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...you enter a corner while skidding\Nand minimize the slide at the exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.79,0:19:48.37,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the fastest manner,\Nand it looks cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.37,0:19:52.33,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.\NYou must've studied a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.53,0:19:56.85,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I had lots of time until my S13 returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.85,0:19:59.25,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I studied by reading a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.68,0:20:02.13,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to try the sidespin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.13,0:20:04.17,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.17,0:20:08.06,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got the hang of it,\Nso I'll move to the next step.
